'''鈷藍色'''又稱'''回回青'''是[[藍色|藍色]]之一，由CoAl<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>產生（[[鈷|鈷]]是一種自然[[金屬|金屬]]）而得名。一些藍色[[玻璃|玻璃]]窗亦為鈷藍色，而其他的則呈[[祖母綠|祖母綠]]。[[世嘉|世嘉]]的[[刺猬索尼克系列|音速小子]]即為鈷藍色。<ref>{{cite web|last=Sheffield|first=Brandon|title=Out of the Blue: Naoto Ohshima Speaks|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/4208/out_of_the_blue_naoto_ohshima_.php?page=2|publisher=Gamasutra|access-date=12 August 2013|quote=Well, he's blue because that's Sega's more-or-less official company color|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716002842/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/4208/out_of_the_blue_naoto_ohshima_.php?page=2|archive-date=16 July 2015}}</ref>

